  Abstract                 = {This paper present the core components of the Semantic Sensor Web: Semantic Web and SWE, Ontology and optionally Rule-Based Reasoning. It also presents a few use cases and topics for future research: Real-time Search in Semantic Sensor Web, Ontology Construction for Semantic Sensor Web, Data Fusion in Semantic Sensor Web, Semantic Annotations in semantic Sensor Web, and Application Developments methodology for Semantic Sensor Web.

